---
title: "Benchmarking Pv3Rs"
---

"Benchmarking Pv3Rs" is a pdf vignette. At present, pkgdown (the R
package used to create this website) does not support pdf vignettes; see
[pkgdown issue 781](https://github.com/r-lib/pkgdown/issues/781). Please access
"Benchmarking Pv3Rs" by installing Pv3Rs and calling
`vignette(topic = "benchmarking", package = "Pv3Rs")` in R.
